gobblin.writer.commands

Interface JdbcWriterCommands

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JdbcBufferedInserter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MySqlWriterCommands, TeradataWriterCommands

    public interface JdbcWriterCommands
extends JdbcBufferedInserter
    JdbcWriterCommands is interface that its implementation will directly talk with underlying RDBMS via JDBC. Different RDBMS may use different SQL syntax, and having this interface decouples JdbcWriter with any syntax difference each RDBMS might have.
